domain_theory

A Lean 4 formalization of Dana Scott's domain theory via Scott Information
Systems, with an accompanying paper.

    This work: https://github.com/catskillsresearch/domain_theory

The mathematics follows Dana Scott, "Domains for Denotational Semantics"
(ICALP, 1982), and the compact presentation of information systems in
Glynn Winskel, "The Formal Semantics of Programming Languages" (Chapter 8).

